-left: 0.3em; padding-right: 0.3em; padding-top: 0.3em; vertical-align: top;"><a href="http://www.blogger.com/wiki/SyntaxHighlighter:Brushes:VB" style="color: #1b8dc1;" title="SyntaxHighlighter:Brushes:VB">Visual Basic</a></td><td style="border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 187, 164); border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; padding-left: 0.3em; padding-right: 0.3em; padding-top: 0.3em; vertical-align: top;">vb, vbnet</td><td style="border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 187, 164); border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; padding-left: 0.3em; padding-right: 0.3em; padding-top: 0.3em; vertical-align: top;">shBrushVb.js</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 187, 164); border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; padding-left: 0.3em; padding-right: 0.3em; padding-top: 0.3em; vertical-align: top;"><a href="http://www.blogger.com/wiki/SyntaxHighlighter:Brushes:XML" style="color: #1b8dc1;" title="SyntaxHighlighter:Brushes:XML">XML</a></td><td style="border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 187, 164); border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; padding-left: 0.3em; padding-right: 0.3em; padding-top: 0.3em; vertical-align: top;">xml, xhtml, xslt, html, xhtml</td><td style="border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 187, 164); border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; padding-left: 0.3em; padding-right: 0.3em; padding-top: 0.3em; vertical-align: top;">shBrushXml.js</td></tr></tbody></table><a href="http://www.blogger.com/post-create.g?blogID=5998578522192555089" name="Don.27t_see_yours.3F" style="color: #1b8dc1;"></a><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">如果找不到自己要用的語言?</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">不用擔心</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">這裡還有:&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.undermyhat.org/blog/2009/09/list-of-brushes-syntaxhighligher/"><span style="font-size: small;">http://www.undermyhat.org/blog/2009/09/list-of-brushes-syntaxhighligher/</span></a><br /><span style="font-size: small;"><br /></span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">首先我們先加入&nbsp;SyntaxHighlighter 的核心元件</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">請到 Layout -&gt; Edit HTML 找出以下標籤</span><br /><br /><pre class="brush: html">&lt;/head&gt;<br /></pre><br /><span style="font-size: small;">然後將以下的 HTML 貼在標籤之前</span><br /><br /><pre class="brush: html">&lt;link href='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/styles/shCore.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'/&gt; <br />&lt;link href='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/styles/shCore.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'/&gt;<br /></pre><br /><span style="font-size: small;">現在在上面的表格選擇你要使用的語言</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">例如: 你需要使用 C++ 就加上以下的標籤</span><br /><br /><pre class="brush: html">&lt;script src='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/shBrushCpp.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt;<br /></pre><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Java 則加入以下的 Code</span><br /><br /><pre class="brush: html">&lt;script src='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/shBrushCpp.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt;<br /></pre><br /><span style="font-size: small;">如果不想太麻煩</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">可以一次加入所有語言</span><br /><br /><pre class="brush: html">&lt;script src='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/shBrushCpp.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt; <br />&lt;script src='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/shBrushCSharp.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt; <br />&lt;script src='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/shBrushCss.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt; <br />&lt;script src='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/shBrushJava.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt; <br />&lt;script src='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/shBrushJScript.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt; <br />&lt;script src='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/shBrushPhp.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt; <br />&lt;script src='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/shBrushPython.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt; <br />&lt;script src='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/shBrushRuby.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt; <br />&lt;script src='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/shBrushSql.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt; <br />&lt;script src='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/shBrushVb.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt; <br />&lt;script src='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/shBrushXml.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt; <br />&lt;script src='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/shBrushPerl.js' type='text/javascript'&gt;&lt;/script&gt;<br /></pre><br />選擇 Theme (主題)<br />只能選擇以下一種<br /><br /><pre class="brush: html">&lt;link href='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/styles/shThemeDefault.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'/&gt; <br /></pre><br /><pre class="brush: html">&lt;link href='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/styles/shThemeDjango.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'/&gt; <br /></pre><br /><pre class="brush: html">&lt;link href='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/styles/shThemeEclipse.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'/&gt; <br /></pre><br /><pre class="brush: html">&lt;link href='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/styles/shThemeEmacs.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'/&gt; <br /></pre><br /><pre class="brush: html">&lt;link href='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/styles/shThemeFadeToGrey.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'/&gt; <br /></pre><br /><pre class="brush: html">&lt;link href='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/styles/shThemeMidnight.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'/&gt; <br /></pre><br /><pre class="brush: html">&lt;link href='http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/styles/shThemeRDark.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'/&gt; <br /></pre><br /><span style="font-size: small;">最後加入下的程式碼便完成了</span><br /><br /><pre class="brush: html">&lt;script language='javascript'&gt; <br />SyntaxHighlighter.config.bloggerMode = true;<br />SyntaxHighlighter.config.clipboardSwf = 'http://alexgorbatchev.com/pub/sh/2.1.364/scripts/clipboard.swf';<br />SyntaxHighlighter.all();<br />&lt;/script&gt;<br /></pre><br /><span style="font-size: small;">測試方法:</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">在網誌內輸入</span><br /><pre class="brush: js; html-script: true">&lt;pre class="brush: js"&gt;<br />alert("Hello World");<br />&lt;/pre&gt;<br /></pre><br /><span style="font-size: small;">如果出現以下效果便成功了</span><br /><pre class="brush: js">alert("Hello World");<br /></pre><br />相關書籍:&nbsp;<a href="http://www.amazon.com/Google-Blogger-Dummies-Computer-Tech/dp/0470407425?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=program06-20&amp;link_code=bil&amp;camp=213689&amp;creative=392969" imageanchor="1" target="_blank"><img alt="Google Blogger For Dummies (For Dummies (Computer/Tech))" src="http://ws.amazon.com/widgets/q?MarketPlace=US&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;WS=1&amp;Format=_SL160_&amp;ASIN=0470407425&amp;tag=program06-20" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.amazon.com/Blogger-Customize-templates-advertising-Technologies/dp/184719317X?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=program06-20&amp;link_code=bil&amp;camp=213689&amp;creative=392969" imageanchor="1" target="_blank"><img alt="Blogger: Beyond the Basics: Customize and promote your blog with original templates, analytics, advertising, and SEO (From Technologies to Solutions)" src="http://ws.amazon.com/widgets/q?MarketPlace=US&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;WS=1&amp;Format=_SL160_&amp;ASIN=184719317X&amp;tag=program06-20" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.amazon.com/Publishing-Blog-Blogger-Visual-QuickProject/dp/0321637526?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=program06-20&amp;link_code=bil&amp;camp=213689&amp;creative=392969" imageanchor="1" target="_bl